# Library & Tooling Rules

## Approved Libraries

### UI

- shadcn/ui
- Tailwind CSS
- lucide-react (icons)

### Forms & Validation

- react-hook-form
- zod

### Backend

- Prisma
- PostgreSQL
- NextAuth

### Images

- UploadThing OR Cloudinary (choose ONE)

### AI

- FASHN API ONLY (until explicitly replaced)

## Library Usage Rules

- Do NOT introduce a library without justification.
- Prefer native platform features.
- Avoid overlapping libraries (e.g., multiple form libs).

## Prisma Rules

- No raw SQL unless absolutely required.
- Use relations properly.
- Always add indexes for searchable fields.
- Migrations must be descriptive.

## Environment Variables

- Never hardcode secrets.
- All env vars must be documented.
- Use `.env.example`.
